desc.en: Bonsaton is a virtual city I built in City Skyline2. This map is for showing the public rail transport system of the city Bonsaton. The system is named TFM. TFM stands for Transporte Ferroviário de Massas de Bonsaton which means Mass Transit Rail of Bonsaton.

reference: 爱发电,Mon Mar 17 2025 22:13:23 GMT+0800 (中國標準時間)
